      "title": "Analysis And Decision",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "id": "b09-c01-p02",
          "type": "prose",
          "body_md": "Use the diagram as a thinking board. Ask what is forcing, what is loose, and what changes after the move. Strong players do not only see a move; they see the reason the move works."
        },
